author: sviens
msg: Fix for bug# JUDDI-27.  The find_tModel and get_tModelDetail functions have been updated to ignore TModels that have been marked as deleted.  A TModel is said to be deleted when the DELETED column of it's corresponding row in the TMODEL table is NOT NULL.
